
## Release text

```text
Busylight MQTT is a local Home Assistant OS add-on for controlling a Kuando / Plenom Busylight Alpha over MQTT.

It listens on an MQTT topic and forwards commands to the Busylight using busylight-for-humans, making it easy to use in Home Assistant automations, dashboards, meeting indicators, streaming workflows, and other status-light setups.

Currently tested with:
- Kuando / Plenom Busylight Alpha
- USB ID: 27bb:3bca
- Home Assistant OS